# C.A.S

C.A.S is a lightweight browser-based project built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It runs entirely on the client side and requires no backend or installation.

## Live Demo
https://s3h4nsa.github.io/c.a.s/

## Features
- Simple and clean interface
- Built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- Fast and lightweight
- Works on any modern browser

## Project Structure

```
c.a.s/
│
├── index.html   # Main page
├── style.css    # Styles and layout
├── script.js    # JavaScript functionality
└── README.md    # Project documentation
```

## How to Run

### Option 1: Open directly
1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open the folder
3. Double-click `index.html`

### Option 2: Using Git

```bash
git clone https://github.com/s3h4nsa/c.a.s.git
cd c.a.s
```

Then open `index.html` in your browser.

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

